{"tid":1424953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再有人被拉 , 請以後女士離狗一百米 , 男士離狗五十米","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:16:40.000Z","uid":15205,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19ce81325aac582553ffd03930c29b1d2650a45f","tid":1424953,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"而家已經進入濫捕時代 , <br />\n唔好再相信班狗會同你對話 , <br />\n頭先深水埗班街坊就係咁中伏 , <br />\n以為同你傾 , 突然間話三點鐘方向 , <br />\n警犬前線就衝即刻拉十幾人 , <br />\n我希望你哋一定要同狗保持距離 ,<br />\n我哋成本高過班狗好多 ,<br />\n我哋既資源係自己或市民既將來/錢 ,<br />\n但最重要一樣野 , <br />\n我哋被人拉一個抗爭既人就少一個 ,<br />\n請與狗保持距離 , <br />\n人多可硬碰 , <br />\n人小 be water , <br />\n求下你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5785827c46a2215c4794f3201614e4a14bd9fae2","tid":1424953,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1077ea484ed9a6362c7591e439b69c8db14984","tid":1424953,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa755b7c9502918632dbe21cc200f8541e7e9326","tid":1424953,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"請與瘋狗保持距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d88d6cd150b561ea00a77aded61df9f96458e6","tid":1424953,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"求求你哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><